title: This Is Why You Can’t Find Lasting Love - with Hayley Quinn
description:
Jillian answers your questions on everything from building muscle, exercises for glute strength, when to take certain supplements and if you can help your body absorb them, microbiome, and understanding water weight. Then, world-renowned dating coach Hayley Quinn is back! She’s helping us learn how to escape our fantasies about love in order to find love that lasts!

Send your questions for Hayley to JillianPodcast@gmail.com

Guest Links:

30 Days of Dating Challenge and HQ Club: https://hayleyquinnclub.com
